{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji24.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给毛岸英的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给毛岸英的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年4月29日）岸英儿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们到了石家庄。岸青有信给你，是俄文，原文临行掉了，兹将译文附上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝你工作顺利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四八年四月二十九日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1948年4月22日，西北野战军收复延安。毛岸英听到消息后，心情异常激动，他多么想去看看父亲啊！正当他翘首西望时，毛泽东已离开陕北，进入晋察冀解放区。在万里征程中，毛泽东给儿子写了这封信。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1948,"month":4,"day":29}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":241,"page_end":241},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}